cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image enhancement. It may also belong to multimedia (cs.MM) as it deals with low light images. The use of deep learning networks suggests it may also belong to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the potential benefits of the method for face detection suggest it may also belong to graphics (cs.GR) sub-category.
